PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780067467
OL,3,CAll remaining sidecar action cancelled
OL,4,Cat Isle of Man TT following crash
OL,6,FOrganisers say an 'immediate technical
OL,7,Fand operational review' was
OL,8,Fimplemented, and the results has led
OL,9,Fto the cancellation of the class for
OL,10,Fthe remainder of this year's event.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the event said:
OL,13,F'This precautionary measure has been
OL,14,Fimplemented in the interests of
OL,15,Fcompetitor and spectator safety and
OL,16,Freflects the Race Organisation's
OL,17,Fcommitment to reviewing all aspects of
OL,18,Fevent safety and operational delivery
OL,19,Fwhenever an incident occurs.'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1780067467
OL,3,CAll remaining sidecar action cancelled
OL,4,Cat Isle of Man TT following crash
OL,6,FAll sidecar competitors and teams
OL,7,Finvolved in the event have been
OL,8,Fbriefed by officials on the outcome of
OL,9,Fthe initial review, and the next
OL,10,Fstages of the assessment process.
OL,12,FConcluding the statement, organisers
OL,13,Fsaid: "We recognise the long-standing
OL,14,Fhistory of Sidecar racing at the TT,
OL,15,Ftogether with the commitment of the
OL,16,Fcompetitors, teams and supporters
OL,17,Finvolved in the class.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
